								<xs:documentation>The LossOfCompetitiveAdvantage field is optional and characterizes (at a high level) the level of impact based on loss of competitive advantage that occured in the Incident including loss/damage/exposure of IP, corporate wisdom, ability to compete, key personnel, etc.</xs:documentation>
